{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "寂靜長廊的兩端", "storyInfo": "在若麥的夢境中，若麥放棄了當鼓手，轉而進入龍門的演藝圈。每天辛苦磨練演技，趕赴各種商務活動的她似乎並不快樂。原本好不容易空出來的休息時間，又被與空合作的綜藝填滿。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g10_dreamcastlestage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>數千數萬雙眼睛之下，如人偶一般，動彈不得。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>去到他們要求我去往之處，發出他們期望我發出之聲。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我，毋畏愛意。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_m", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經兩天兩夜沒有見到人煙了……", "name": "迷途的少女"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龍門……龍門到底在哪裡？家在哪裡？", "name": "迷途的少女"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸、媽媽……我好渴……好累……", "name": "迷途的少女"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$2"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處的……是高樓嗎？", "name": "迷途的少女"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$2"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快要到了……還不能睡……", "name": "迷途的少女"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "迷途的少女"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g7_filmandtvstudio", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若麥小姐，實在是太精彩了！我心裡想要的完全就是這種感覺！", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平凡的鄉村少女決然拋下所有，踏上了追尋音樂夢想的旅程。", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場戲拍的就是她人生中最低潮的時候，從此以後，她便會遇到賞識自己的貴人，成為龍門最受歡迎的樂手。", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝導演誇獎~", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在看這個劇本的時候，我意外地很能理解女主角的心境。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那當然！這個劇本、這個角色就是為若麥小姐你量身打造的啊！", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*尚蜀方言*明明是為了搶新年檔期，臨時修改的劇本……", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……？", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "投資人眼紅《少女鼓手》票房表現亮眼，指定由你來主演我們這部電影。", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後你的經紀公司要求電影必須在新年檔期上映，導演逼我一週內改完劇本……", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本的結局……應該是少女在彌留之際，做了一個分不清真假的夢。", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一片眩光中，資質平平的少女搖搖晃晃地走上了領獎台。", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平凡的少女在夢裡贏得了所有人的認可，也終於和一切達成了和解。", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才是這部片該有的、令人感覺諷刺的結局啊！", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*龍門粗口*，你那個爛劇本，如果沒若麥小姐的加持，怎麼可能拿到這麼多贊助跟支持？", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰在乎你的那些贊助跟支持啊？我看你就是捧金主捧習慣了，忘了自己的藝術理想！", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現實裡哪有那麼美好的事情，普通人怎麼可能有機會走到萬眾矚目的舞台前？！", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*尚蜀方言*你不是來自鄉下的，當然不會懂啊！但我是，我懂啊！", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡的傢伙，看我怎麼收拾你——", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp5"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02", "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "言語的交鋒之間，兩人的距離越來越近，口舌之爭最終演變成了肢體衝突。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們有話好好說……", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你拍的那些爛鏡頭，我早*尚蜀粗口*就想吐槽了！", "name": "編劇"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你等著瞧，等我飛黃騰達之後，*龍門粗口*第一個就把你踢掉！", "name": "導演"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#4$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？不是——！", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#4$3"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "c", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_deluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫院剛剛通知我，說編劇和導演被分到同一間病房，兩個人的病床正好面對面。", "name": "助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過幸好兩個人都戴了護頸，現在只能互相乾瞪眼而已。", "name": "助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩的是，短時間內這部電影應該是拍不了了……", "name": "助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正最近都沒有好好休息過，現在這樣說不定剛好~", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等後續的拍攝計劃確定後我會再聯絡你，這段時間要麻煩你先保持隨時待命的狀態了。", "name": "助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）唉，不知道為什麼，感覺輕鬆一點了……", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行不行，還不能放鬆下來——", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽……？", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trnpndor", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rooftop_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少女拿起電話，推開拉門，走到了陽台上。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*若麥，吃過晚餐了嗎？最近忙不忙呢？", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*吃過了。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*最近家裡的小麥又豐收了，我們每天一大早就要出門，忙到太陽下山才能收工。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*唉，不是早就跟你們說過了嗎？你們就好好在鄉下享福吧。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*還不是怕你太累，如果真的很累，回家休息一下也可以啊。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*對了，今年過年你想吃什麼？我和你爸提前準備一下……", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*過年不可能有時間回家啦！大家最輕鬆的時候，就是我最忙的時候……", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*方言*是這樣哦……", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（微弱的聲音）媽媽，姐姐終於接電話了？", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（漸近的跑步聲）", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐！我們有在電視上看到你的新電影的預告片哦！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜我們這邊沒有電影院，不然就去買票支持你了！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，沒關係啦。等之後出了碟片，我寄一份回去給你們。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#8$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好——！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你在電影裡打鼓的樣子真的好帥哦！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最近也開始練爵士鼓了，用的就是你以前那組舊鼓。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在爵士鼓是不是打得越來越厲害了？我以後也想像你一樣在舞台上演出！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……嘿嘿，最近有點忙，沒有時間練習啦。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我是不會忘記練習的，我們要一起加油哦！", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！媽媽叫我們去睡覺了，姐姐也要早點休息哦！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都要注意身體喔！晚安！", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚安！", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_phonestop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ringoff", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若麥小姐，剛剛公司臨時通知，有一個大型綜藝節目想邀請你去參加。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間是明晚八點開始，預計會錄製到第二天的凌晨。請問這個時間可以嗎？", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#4$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太突然了吧…… ", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#4$3"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#4$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原因是……他們請的另一位嘉賓，是偶像明星空小姐。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對方和我們的人氣旗鼓相當，而且空小姐在圈內外的評價都很不錯。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個很好的曝光機會，機會難得，雖然時間有點趕，但公司還是推薦你去參加一下……", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你就回覆——若麥希望能跟大家合作愉快。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，那麼今天的工作就都結束了。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚安，若麥小姐，祝你有個好夢。", "name": "電話裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……至少今天終於能睡個好覺了。）", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_phonestop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "nw1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "nw1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trnclsdor", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_deluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.2}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她抬頭看向茶几上的電子鐘，上面的時間是“00:23”。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她重重地倒在了沙發上，身體很快陷了進去，她被牢牢地包住。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有幾個月沒練鼓了……？", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若麥拖著腳步走到電子鼓前，鈸片上已經覆蓋了一層薄薄的灰塵。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我的鼓棒放到哪裡了啊？", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上一次拿起鼓棒的情形，也有點記不起來了。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是在家裡？還是更早以前在《少女鼓手》的片場？"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了，看一下電視再睡吧。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "slide1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "slide1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "粉絲朋友們大家好，我是新人演員若麥！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最新主演的電影《少女鼓手》正在上映中！這是一部特別有趣的電影，推薦大家去電影院觀賞哦！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_result", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的夢想是成為龍門第一——不，泰拉第一的鼓手！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#3$4"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和若麥一起，成為最想成為的自己吧~", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$4"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是專業人士，有些東西總是要捨棄掉的……沒錯。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#1$4"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}